  <h3 class="welcome-title ">PDFind</h3><br/>
  <h3 class="welcome-subtitle">
    PDFind scans your Gmail inbox, and prints a list of all pdf attachments found.
    </br> You can filter, sort, and search the list for a certain pdf or a group of pdfs.
    </br> Once you've found the pdf that you are looking for, 
    </br> you can click the name to view and download the given attachment!
  </h3> </br>
  <div>
    <a class="btn btn-outline-dark" href="/help" role="button">
